{"lemma":"خَفْقَةٌ","slug":"خَفْقَةٌ","root":"خ.ف.ق","root_slug":"خ-ف-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ف-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n11128"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%8E%D9%81%D9%92%D9%82%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n11128","headword_ar":"خَفْقَةٌ","root":"xfq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A single nodding of the head, by reason of drowsiness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dozing"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: see 1, in two places: (Mgh, Msb:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a slight,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"light, sleep."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) It is said in a trad. respecting Ed-Dejjál [or Antichrist],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaxoruju fiY xafoqapK mina Ald~iyni","text_ar":"يَخْرُجُ فِى خَفْقَةٍ مِنَ الدِّينِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", explained as meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He will come forth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a time when religion will be drowsy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dozing, by reason of weakness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDaY xafoqapN mina All~ayoli","text_ar":"مَضَى خَفْقَةٌ مِنَ اللَّيْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A period"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAEapN","text_ar":"سَاعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the night passed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK.) ―         -b3-  And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sayoru All~ayoli AlxafoqataAni wasayoru Aln~ahaAri","text_ar":"سَيْرُ اللَّيْلِ الخَفْقَتَانِ وَسَيْرُ النَّهَارِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlbarodaAni","text_ar":"البَرْدَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[The time of]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the journeying of the night is the first part thereof and the last part thereof, and"},{"kind":"text","text":"[that of]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the journeying of the day is the morning, between daybreak and sunrise, and the evening, between sunset and nightfall."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-  See also the next paragraph, in two places."}],"source_refs":["Mgh","Msb"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}